"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/828242","Scotland Office","false","2018-01-25","<p>Keith Cochrane attended nine meetings of the Joint Management Board between December 2015 and December 2017.</p>","Dumfriesshire, Clydesdale and Tweeddale","David Mundell",,"2018-01-25T13:16:46.32Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/828242/answer","Biography information for David Mundell","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/828242/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/828242/answer",,,,,"2","Scotland","Scotland","2018-01-22","Scotland Office: Keith Cochrane","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Scotland, how many meetings he had with Keith Cochrane during his term as a member of the Joint Management Board of his Department.","false","Biography information for Ged Killen","Rutherglen and Hamilton West","Ged Killen","124202"
