"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/825514","Home Office","false","2018-01-23","<p>The number of incidents of unauthorised sharing of asylum information and the amount of compensation paid by the department for unauthorised sharing of asylum information is not held in a format which is reportable.</p><p>It is contrary to Home Office policy to disclose information on individual asylum cases.</p>","Romsey and Southampton North","Caroline  Nokes","123653","2018-01-23T15:49:20.473Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/825514/answer","Biography information for Caroline Nokes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/825514/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/825514/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2018-01-18","Asylum: Disclosure of Information","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, how many incidents of unauthorised sharing of asylum information there have been in her Department in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Afzal Khan","Manchester, Gorton","Afzal Khan","123652"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/825515","Home Office","false","2018-01-23","<p>The number of incidents of unauthorised sharing of asylum information and the amount of compensation paid by the department for unauthorised sharing of asylum information is not held in a format which is reportable.</p><p>It is contrary to Home Office policy to disclose information on individual asylum cases.</p>","Romsey and Southampton North","Caroline  Nokes","123652","2018-01-23T15:49:20.533Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/825515/answer","Biography information for Caroline Nokes","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/825515/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/825515/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2018-01-18","Asylum: Disclosure of Information","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, how much her Department has paid in compensation as a result of its unauthorised sharing of asylum information since 2010.","false","Biography information for Afzal Khan","Manchester, Gorton","Afzal Khan","123653"
